con:eventHandlers.name: RequestFilter.filterRequest
con:eventHandlers.con:script: if( request.requestContent == null ) return log.info "Old request with CDATA : " + request.requestContent def requestContent = request.requestContent requestContent = requestContent.replaceAll( "<!\\[CDATA\\[", "" ) requestContent = requestContent.replaceAll( "]]>", "" ) log.info "New request without CDATA : " + request.requestContent request.requestContent = requestContent
